Articles.Content:
Um I made an SSTO. I got into orbit and then sent out Jeb on EVA. When i returned Jeb stayed on the ladder outside but there was also one on the inside.

Here are some screen shots.

http://imgur.com/a/NRmgj

The only mods are KAS and Crew manifest.

Any ideas?

Edited December 23, 2013 by worir4

I have had this happen as well, though not in orbit.

..And another took his place.

Soon, I had a whole stream of Matdas Kermani, with a few of the other guys as well.

http://i.imgur.com/NMwBMZT.png

http://i.imgur.com/YVoMoGA.png

Even had some of the strange stretching seen in your last photo happening, though for me, everything is landed.

I think it could be something to do with crewmanifest, perhaps you should update.
OK thanks. I suppose it was just a one off thing.
